title: Grateful Dead Live at San Francisco Civic Auditorium on 1983-12-28
description:
Set I
Feel Like A Stranger
Dire Wolf
Mama Tried >
Mexicali Blues
Loser
New Minglewood Blues
Bird Song
Set II
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider
Playing In The Band >
Drums >
Space >
The Wheel >
The Other One >
Stella Blue >
Around & Around >
Johnny B. Goode

Encore:
It's All Over Now Baby Blue


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
